Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:08.99,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,It was difficult to write calligraphy on a boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.28,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was a good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.77,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I thought of it as soiling white paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:15.48,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,that made it easy to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:19.20,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, my brush feels less heavy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.16,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one month until the Naruka \NInstitute Calligraphy Exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:24.62,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,With a month, this time I should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:30.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:34.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:35.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:37.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:42.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come bringin' more when you run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:47.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He really does come and \Ngo through the back way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:53.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can eat all \Nthis pickled daikon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:58.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I need to focus on calligraphy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:04.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use a more novel calligraphy style,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:05.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,for an artistic konomon—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:06.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "konomon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:07.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write on konomon—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:11.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "konomon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:13.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Konomon Institute Calligraphy \NExhibition is next month—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "Konomon" Institute Calligraphy Exhibition!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:16.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:17.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:19.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.10,MX Handwritten 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:22.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:40.68,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Barakamon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:58.03,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Un ni Oegii
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.03,Barakamon Title Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Translation: Going Swimming at the Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon... konomon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon... konomon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon... konomon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:05.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:09.76,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come bringin' more when you run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach us calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful rude of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:22.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:27.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grampa said ya can never have \Ntoo much, an' told me to bring this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, help us with our assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, hold the brush in your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This's my right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do calligraphy left-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not impossible, but inkstone \Nplacement and such make it harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.91,MX Calligraphy 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Learning From The Past
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:49.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:53.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll write the example, so watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:55.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}too{\i0} close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't writin' all fuzzy like usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:07.01,MX Calligraphy 3,,0000,0000,0000,,Learning From \NThe Past
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fuzzy"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything begins with the fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna do writin' like {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:11.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's real showy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.27,MX Calligraphy 4,,0000,0000,0000,,MU \N{\i1}(Nil){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm still perfecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's done and acknowledged, \Nthen I'll instruct you in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acknowledged? By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:24.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I win grand prize at the Naruka Institute \NCalligraphy Exhibition next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:29.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it don't win a prize, \Nit looks plenty good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:33.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of fussin' over that stuff, \NI'd rather have fun writin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:35.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You three really are kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you'll write this, Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! "Cat"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:48.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm your teacher, \Nyou'll definitely win prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you do, you're sure to understand why
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I care so much about winning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:58.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll write for one full hour, starting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:03.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't apply ink twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That stroke shouldn't trail off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:11.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It should stop short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm pooped!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all of you! No slacking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who asked for my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get less than grand prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:32.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But how many times are ya gonna make \Nus write the same thing over and over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a trick to writing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think it's simple for \Nprofessionals to write beautifully?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:43.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to understand the passion that \Ngoes into a single sheet of calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:45.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousands, millions, of predecessors
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,have committed trillions, quadrillions, \Nof thoughts to paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:52.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite physical fatigue and mental breakdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You face the solitude single-mindedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the utmost limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see the utmost limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Utmost limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With each step...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With each step, you get closer to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:08.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet an endless desert still stretches before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can walk no further. \NYou're tired of writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:13.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you think that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, even that god is just \Nanother mirage in the desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:25.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never seen anyone hallucinate \Nover calligraphy before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:30.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't wanna go that far just \Nfor a middle school assignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go buy us some drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:34.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you guys had no motivation—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We do, so let us rest already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure you keep practicing until I return!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:49.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's an honest-to-goodness calligraphy nut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:49.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no way he can get a girlfriend like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He could have a long-distance relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.18,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:01.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll snoop around the room for evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out. That's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:09.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could be his girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Miwa-chan, don't just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you so interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A commemorative photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's datin' one of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:22.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:25.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty, but she's standing kinda far from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't she too plain to be Sensei's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would her looks matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:35.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she can talk about \Ncalligraphy, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:38.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya really think there's a woman \Nwho'd listen to his delusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:38.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By golly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just listening, \Neven a monkey could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:43.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:47.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei said this's his treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture frame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet there's a picture of his sweetheart in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:55.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't believe Sensei's a married woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, that's not how you use that phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru sure does love Sensei a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:10.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At his age, it'd be weirder \Nif he'd never dated a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:14.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In another ten years, \Nyou'll be the beauty, Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can appropriate him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Up-rope-ree-ate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At Sensei's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.56,MX Calligraphy 5,,0000,0000,0000,,Su \NShi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought your drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you girls doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't straighten up, you won't \Nwin anything, much less grand prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already 23 years old, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at other things besides calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you thinkin', gettin' \Nturned on by historical figures?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you should go out with Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:49.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By golly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me! I'll up-rope-ree-ate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sto—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:56.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer gonna die alone at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Up-rope-ree-ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An ocean swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:10.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are going on a trip to the beach, \Nand I'd like you to chaperone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:14.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked their teacher first, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.43,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm goin' fishin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:20.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They all can swim, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just have to watch them, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Miwa and Tama are going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make sure they don't \Ndo anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:35.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having our Hiroshi go \Nalong, too, just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:37.34,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This sounds like a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:40.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:45.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:45.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Butt j—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:47.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't run around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miwa-nee and Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin', Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer late, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:58.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:01.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those look like gym clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:03.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just "like" 'em. They {\i1}are{\i0} gym clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the best for swimmin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're swimming in those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it hard to swim in regular clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You strip down if ya like, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, I don't have a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! I said to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:20.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro isn't here ye—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:29.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, kids, stick with Hiro-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.69,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's just coming for fun, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I'm gonna master the backstroke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't race around too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We come to this beach every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:52.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too rocky to be a beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Play somewhere safer, like a sandy beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sandy beaches are for little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:01.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The footing... is really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:11.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is what's wrong with city slickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He oughta be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone uses this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, dive in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:24.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:30.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, those're big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea urchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea urchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:33.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Find any neat fish, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but the goggles keep \Nfogging up and I can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, wipe it with mugwort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep mugwort leaves in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mugwort extract helps prevent foggin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, you know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like Gramma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:06.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What d'ya mean, "Gramma"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry... You didn't like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, that's the problem with kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They just dunno how to enjoy the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see one! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:29.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:32.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah! It's an octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-nii, yer so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:45.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-nii, yer so uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:51.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, boys just dunno \Nhow to play at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Miwa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go overdoin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rest a bit over by Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:05.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is red!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:16.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more the indoors type.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the indoors type, then settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some water for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:24.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:34.84,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? I feel like \Nshe's really staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:40.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever been so worried about \Nsomething, you couldn't sleep at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not worried, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be frank. What do you think about Hiro-nii?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:54.48,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.89,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.25,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.25,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what I think of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.20,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:02.36,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's close in age, and easy to talk \Nto, so... like a brother, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.79,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No... we're not that close.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:09.07,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just the guy who brings me my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.30,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:13.03,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would this glasses girl \Nbe asking me such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.00,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.62,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have a crush on Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:22.46,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it. That's why she's \Nbeen acting so odd lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:28.01,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm not perfect, she still sees \Nme as a mentor, and wants my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.48,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She does have her cute side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:31.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.04,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll support them as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro's a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's thoughtful, a good cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't often see such a great young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the perfect guy to go out w—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:51.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think it is that \NI'm having these sleepless nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:55.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not one of those nasty fujoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fujoshi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:57.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:58.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:14:59.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangero—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sen... sei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:10.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sea slug!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah! You're pretty daring to grab that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:15.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You try holdin' it, Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can hold it, yer an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:22.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:27.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-nee, yer mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:30.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer face makes me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gross, but it's fine once ya get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all squishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. That means yer an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-nii, how's Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:50.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:53.83,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! How useless can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:55.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:57.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go someplace real fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someplace real fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, one that only adults can go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:11.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I blacked out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should probably head back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had lunch yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:29.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still playin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew they'd complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Naru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:36.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was with Miwa-chan just a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:37.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:47.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:58.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:00.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's sayin' something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:03.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After one more jump, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:07.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:08.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:20.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:39.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You done good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my protégé for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I jumped, I heard Sensei cheerin' me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He yelled, "Naru!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wasn't scared at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheering?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, \Nhe was sayin' somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did nothing but dangerous stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:10.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't do it no more, so don't be mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, c'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:35.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I came to this island, all I ever \Nreally had to worry about was myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:40.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've been \Nso worried about someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:47.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:49.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:52.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I won't make you worry again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:54.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:56.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do nothin' dangerous no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:06.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Sensei! Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:10.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The outsider's totally one of the gang now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.50,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect me to join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.05,MX Signs 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,600)}Sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:17.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:18.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.18,MX Signs 4,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool \NBreeze
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.57,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Missed Call   1\NKawafuji
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:44.53,MX Signs 3,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukue Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No use...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not answering his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:49.04,MX Signs 5,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of \NRange
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of range again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, this place is inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like everything is miniature. Teeny-weeny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:00.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke, are you making fun of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:02.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to meet Handa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:46.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-chan! Miwa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:50.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair's really wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:55.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cuz it's been so humid lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You always did have unruly hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.46,MX Handwritten,,0000,0000,0000,,Scruffy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:01.75,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:04.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you girls come to fish, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:07.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, your hair is intense...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:08.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets like this when I'm in good condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:12.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, ain't it 'cuz of the humidity?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:15.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You both have similar hair qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:16.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your hairstyle's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:19.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, don't copy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:20.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Copy"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:22.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe try goin' close-cropped?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:24.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't look good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:27.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's a bunch here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:30.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if yer teacher joins ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.33,MX Handwritten,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1)}Scruffy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:34.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, it's tough when it's this muggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:37.11,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as the teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.11,0:22:38.80,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So glad I have straight hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:40.08,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Just close-cropped isn't enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:40.79,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:45.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got tengusa head!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:46.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:49.97,MX Signs 6,,0000,0000,0000,,Tengusa\N{\i1}(red algae){\i0}
